Since number 1 promotes a direct and strong style of conveyance, it’s ideal for someone in a rather high position, think managerial, supervisory, or leading business role. With this number, you’ll find it easier to be assertive and your verbal functions will improve tremendously.

Plus, not only will you be able to make tough decisions in the blink of an eye, but you’ll also be an excellent debater—someone who can put forth convincing arguments or a stronger case without batting an eyelid.
